{"tid":1225071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好衝呀！！唔好衝呀！！","createTime":"2019-06-15T06:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T06:29:05.000Z","uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"115ebc8e06333e81f46d2bf959930e49396af94c","tid":1225071,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:23:05.000Z","msg":"如果唔和平示威一來人數少，二來義士比人捉左可能會坐幾年監，影響前途。同埋警察會專登挑釁示威者，而令前線衝擊，再拉人。社會失去左你地班有識之士，有勇有謀既人實在太過可惜！<br />\n<br />\n反而同其他方法去不合作運動會好好多！<br />\n<br />\n聽日要求釋放被捕人仕！<br />\n暫緩唔係勝利，唔好再打飛機！ <br />\n撤回先係重點！<br />\n<br />\n眼見身邊既人好多都會出席聽日既遊行，證明今次和平既力量比上次雨傘係來得強，千奇唔好比林鄭搵位入。<br />\n<br />\n大家記得7月2號前登記做選民！投鄺俊宇，楊岳橋，郭榮鏗，張超雄等等既人。叫埋你身邊既人投佢地，vote them down ！<br />\n<br />\n記住戰場係未來。<br />\n90 00 後，唔好太衝，<br />\n留返d力同雜總慢慢玩！"},{"pid":"5a480098df5e79bed136e9be7cf1d396f040e2e6","tid":1225071,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa914fa46486ba2fe29363f476187b45eb0ef9d8","tid":1225071,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c669ef07e97510c29230bd7ce6e8738d3f6fb59","tid":1225071,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fa090fbedd2dd81bc9c9708df246de1a2399fdb","tid":1225071,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64079591ea51d627b678cb065bd51e7099ac2d4b","tid":1225071,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:24:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fec8166930dd3fab4c95a388d2aadd0bb8f3565e","tid":1225071,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e12aa9b5335d1aa087f24f01aad36f793ec22fa2","tid":1225071,"uid":147797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acb23effd6b7df7b34e9c185a4332a6c2da4f93c","t